        <abstract> 
<p>Has reduced 20 <hi rend="italic">Cyrena</hi> species to geographical varieties of one species, <hi rend="italic">Cyrena fluminalis</hi>. Hooker is reducing Indian flora at the rate of 19 to 1.</p>  
<p>Recommends W. H. Harvey’s <hi rend="italic">Seaside book</hi> [1849] and Charles Pickering’s <hi rend="italic">Races of man</hi> [1850].</p> 
        </abstract>
